From: Nunchi Operators <nunchi@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:22:47 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] discord: owner-only native-fact sidecar with validated
 directory and self context

Append exact native facts per message to an owner-only sidecar
(STATE_DIR/nunchi-v2/native-events.jsonl): author ID, bot flag, mention
IDs, guild, reply reference, and the EXACT delivered content (attachment
placeholders and voice transcripts included). The containing directory is
validated to be a caller-owned, non-symlink directory with mode 0700
before every write; a pre-existing 0755/0777/symlinked/non-directory path
is rejected fail-closed. The file is created 0600, opened O_NOFOLLOW, and
validated as an owner-owned regular file; an unserializable record is
dropped, never partially written. Self-authored messages are recorded here
as retained context before the waking-path drop, so a V2 consumer keeps
them as SELF_RETAINED_NO_WAKE without a recursive wake.
